<specimenCount box="[825,839,224,248]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
25.9–26.3. Length of tegmina: 
<specimenCount box="[1202,1222,224,248]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
