<specimenCount box="[1324,1338,224,248]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
2.9–3.6. Length of hind femur: 
<specimenCount box="[406,426,260,284]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
10.2–10.3; 
<specimenCount box="[554,568,260,284]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
11.5–12.1.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,151,392]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,295,320]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
